#: ../../source/index.rst:15 a7380644bae5410eaed3bc1141e224df
msgid ""
"A fast, differentiable, JIT-free, and debugging-friendly finite element "
"library — bringing modern PyTorch ergonomics to scientific computing."
msgstr "一个快速、可微、无 JIT 且易于调试的有限元库——将现代 PyTorch 的使用体验带入科学计算。"

#: ../../source/index.rst:18 cbb2be1be2ea4397be173b2dcd32c7a6
msgid ""
"TensorMesh is a finite element method (FEM) library built on PyTorch, "
"designed to solve partial differential equations (PDEs) with elegance and "
"efficiency. By integrating natively with the PyTorch ecosystem, it provides "
"automatic differentiation, GPU acceleration, and an intuitive Pythonic "
"interface — without sacrificing the rigor of classical FEM."
msgstr ""
"TensorMesh 是一个基于 PyTorch 构建的有限元方法（FEM）库，旨在优雅而高效地求解偏微分方程（PDE）。通过与 PyTorch "
"生态原生集成，它在不牺牲经典有限元严谨性的前提下，提供自动微分、GPU 加速以及直观的 Pythonic 接口。"

#: ../../source/index.rst:26 6070de2ca36d429fac86fd3841db63ee
msgid "Core Strengths"
msgstr "核心优势"

#: ../../source/index.rst:28 5b6ced349b074d4eb0693fb442ea9892
msgid ""
"**GPU-Native & Differentiable**: Built on PyTorch from the ground up. Moving"
" an entire FEM workflow to the GPU takes a single line of code — every "
"downstream assembly, solve, and gradient inherits the device automatically, "
"with no separate backend or data-marshalling step. Native autograd flows "
"seamlessly through assembly and solve, enabling end-to-end differentiable "
"PDE pipelines."
msgstr ""
"**GPU 原生与可微**\\ ：完全基于 PyTorch 从底层构建。只需一行代码即可将整个有限元工作流迁移到 "
"GPU——其后续的每一次装配、求解和梯度计算都会自动继承设备，无需单独的后端或数据搬运步骤。原生 autograd "
"可无缝贯穿装配与求解，从而实现端到端可微的 PDE 流水线。"

#: ../../source/index.rst:35 23ef8c68127444de9ce50ec6d997e7fd
msgid ""
"**High-Performance Tensorized Assembly**: A fully tensorized Map-Reduce "
"algorithm powered by `TensorGalerkin <https://arxiv.org/abs/2602.05052>`_, "
"which fuses element-wise operations into monolithic GPU kernels, eliminating"
" Python-level loops and delivering order-of-magnitude speedups over CPU-"
"based FEM stacks."
msgstr ""
"**高性能张量化装配**\\ ：由 `TensorGalerkin <https://arxiv.org/abs/2602.05052>`_ "
"驱动的全张量化 Map-Reduce 算法，将逐单元运算融合为单体的 GPU 内核，消除了 Python 层级的循环，相较于基于 CPU "
"的有限元技术栈带来数量级的加速。"

#: ../../source/index.rst:41 b2d76637dc11495cb3fca3a26b289c47
msgid ""
"**JIT-Free & Debugging-Friendly**: Eager execution with no compilation "
"overhead. Dynamic meshes, adaptive refinement, and interactive workflows "
"just work — no recompilation latency, no opaque traces."
msgstr ""
"**无 JIT 且易于调试**\\ ：即时执行（eager "
"execution），无编译开销。动态网格、自适应加密以及交互式工作流均可开箱即用——没有重新编译的延迟，也没有难以理解的追踪信息。"

#: ../../source/index.rst:45 d8ee1e1fa92346e0a01eb1e2df737970
msgid ""
"**Comprehensive Element & Mesh Support**: Triangular, tetrahedral, pyramid, "
"and prismatic elements with automated mesh generation for common geometries "
"and seamless Gmsh / VTK-HDF5 I/O."
msgstr ""
"**全面的单元与网格支持**\\ ：支持三角形、四面体、四棱锥和三棱柱单元，可为常见几何自动生成网格，并与 Gmsh / VTK-HDF5 实现无缝 "
"I/O。"

#: ../../source/index.rst:49 f8edb38b09ae49898df3561870e024e2
msgid ""
"**Flexible Solvers**: Powered by `torch-sla <https://www.torchsla.com/>`_, "
"our companion library for differentiable sparse linear algebra. Linear, "
"nonlinear, and eigenvalue solvers run across multiple backends on CPU and "
"GPU, with full autograd support, batched solves, and distributed multi-GPU "
"scaling."
msgstr ""
"**灵活的求解器**\\ ：由 `torch-sla <https://www.torchsla.com/>`_ "
"驱动，这是我们配套的可微稀疏线性代数库。线性、非线性和特征值求解器可在 CPU 和 GPU 上跨多种后端运行，并完整支持 "
"autograd、批量求解以及分布式多 GPU 扩展。"

#: ../../source/index.rst:55 6d9e66e24d354272843939ec63e93395
msgid ""
"**Pythonic API**: Custom weak forms in pure Python — no separate DSL, no "
"form compiler. If you can write PyTorch, you can write FEM."
msgstr ""
"**Pythonic API**\\ ：用纯 Python 编写自定义弱形式——无需独立的 DSL，也无需 form 编译器。只要会写 "
"PyTorch，就能写有限元。"

