#: ../../source/index.rst:135 df27fba96ccc48a89b6bebc78cb1ff60
msgid ""
"**Custom Weak Forms (Pythonic)** — supports user-defined bilinear / linear "
"forms directly in Python, without a separate DSL such as UFL. **End-to-End "
"Autograd** — gradients flow natively through the entire pipeline; FEniCS "
"supports this via the external ``dolfin-adjoint`` package. **Maturity** — "
"reflects project age, ecosystem size, and production deployments."
msgstr ""
"**自定义弱形式（Pythonic）**——支持直接在 Python 中定义双线性／线性形式，无需 UFL 等独立的 DSL。\\ **端到端 "
"autograd**——梯度可原生贯穿整个流水线；FEniCS 通过外部的 ``dolfin-adjoint`` 包来支持这一点。\\ "
"**成熟度**——反映项目的存续时间、生态规模以及生产环境部署情况。"

